  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a puzzle game. The game consists of multiple levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The requirements for clearing the level are: you need to find the key in each level and then go to the teleportation gate. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level consists of multiple rooms. If the adjacent boundaries of two adjacent rooms perfectly match, the boundaries of those two rooms will disappear and become passable. Players can move the positions of the rooms to find the corresponding path to complete the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras/f987cd7fda8b214cb816ba5a975d4418.poster.avif?t=1735546168\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras/f987cd7fda8b214cb816ba5a975d4418.webm?t=1735546168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras/f987cd7fda8b214cb816ba5a975d4418.mp4?t=1735546168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The story setting of the game </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A person who has fallen into a deep abyss needs to find a way to escape. There is a mutated moon in the abyss. Players search for ways to repair the moon and escape the abyss as they progress through one level after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras/1db353ddb4bfbbf756ac725cb633578f.avif?t=1735546168\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras_big/1db353ddb4bfbbf756ac725cb633578f.avif?t=1735546168 width=800 height=118 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a puzzle game. The game consists of multiple levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The requirements for clearing the level are: you need to find the key in each level and then go to the teleportation gate. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level consists of multiple rooms. If the adjacent boundaries of two adjacent rooms perfectly match, the boundaries of those two rooms will disappear and become passable. Players can move the positions of the rooms to find the corresponding path to complete the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras/f987cd7fda8b214cb816ba5a975d4418.poster.avif?t=1735546168\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras/f987cd7fda8b214cb816ba5a975d4418.webm?t=1735546168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras/f987cd7fda8b214cb816ba5a975d4418.mp4?t=1735546168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The story setting of the game </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A person who has fallen into a deep abyss needs to find a way to escape. There is a mutated moon in the abyss. Players search for ways to repair the moon and escape the abyss as they progress through one level after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras/1db353ddb4bfbbf756ac725cb633578f.avif?t=1735546168\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394910/extras_big/1db353ddb4bfbbf756ac725cb633578f.avif?t=1735546168 width=800 height=118 /></span></p>",
